(10, '07 Days / 06 Nights Medan - Bukit Lawang Tracking and Rafting - B', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Discover Sumatra Orang Utan &amp; Great Rapids Adventure\r\nof Wampu River rafting</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">A true wilderness experience, see Sumatra Orang Utan and\r\nEnjoy river journey.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Excelent experience and fantastic tracking to see Sumatra\r\nOrang Utan and Rafting at Wampu river</p>\r\n\r\n					                                					                                					                                ', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d15928.53941049041!2d98.13070828719748!3d3.5563903750193124!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3030c81b5f04b997%3A0xd57e31753995db8f!2sBukit%20Lawang%2C%20Kec.%20Bohorok%2C%20Kabupaten%20Langkat%2C%20Sumatera%20Utara!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1572712466323!5m2!1sid!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>', '<div><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>DAY 01: AIRPORT / MEDAN - HOTEL ( EMERALD GARDEN / ASEAN INT HTL)</b></span></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Upon arrival at Kuala Namu Int airport Medan pick up by our tour guide and then transfer to hotel in Medan. Afternoon free at own leisure.</span></div><div><br></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>DAY 02. MEDAN - BUKIT LAWANG (BUKIT LAWANG COTTAGE)</b></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Arrival at Polonia Airport Medan drive to Bukit Lawang with a stop at Crocodile farm, and several Plantation for Rubber and Palm oil arrival at Bukit Lawang check in to the hotel.</span></div><div><br></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>DAY 03.BUKIT LAWANG TRACKING LEUSER PARK. (OVERNIGHT TENT or SHELTER)B.L.D</b></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">After breakfast at the hotel then walking trough the bank of the river and crossing the river