an style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Included :</b><br>-Accommodation based on twin sharing <br>-Air condition private car <br>-Daily breakfast<br>- Tours <br>- Transfers <br>- Entrance fee <br>- English speaking tour guide <br>- Jungle tracking at Bukit Lawang (02 days/01 night) included: local guide, permit, meals and camping equipment <br>- Fullday white water rafting at Wampu River.<br><br><b>Â Excluded : </b><br>- Airfare, Airport tax, Insurance, donation, tips, camera permit at Bukit Lawang and all personal gratuities.<br><br></span></div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    '),
(11, '07 Days / 06 Nights Medan - Bukit Lawang Tracking and Rafting - A', 'Discover Sumatra Orang Utan &amp; Great Rapids Adventure of Wampu River rafting<br>A true wilderness experience, see Sumatra Orang Utan and Enjoy river journey.<br>Excelent experience and fantastic tracking to see Sumatra Orang Utan and Rafting at Wampu river<br>					                                					                                ', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d15928.53941049041!2d98.13070828719748!3d3.5563903750193124!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3030c81b5f04b997%3A0xd57e31753995db8f!2sBukit%20Lawang%2C%20Kec.%20Bohorok%2C%20Kabupaten%20Langkat%2C%20Sumatera%20Utara!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1572712466323!5m2!1sid!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>', '<div align=\"justify\"><b>DAY 01. MEDAN - BUKIT LAWANG (ECOLODGE BUKIT LAWANG COTTAGE)</b></div><div align=\"justify\">Arrival at Kuala Namu Int airport Medan drive to Bukit Lawang with a stop at Crocodile farm, and several Plantation for Rubber and Palm oil arrival at Bukit Lawang check in to the hotel.</div><div align=\"justify\"><br></div><div align=\"justify\"><b>DAY 02.BUKIT LAWANG TRACKING LEUSER PARK. (OVERNIGHT TENT or SHELTER)B.L.D</b></div><div align=\"justify\">After breakfast at the hotel then walking trough the bank of the river and crossing the river by traditional canoe and walking up the jungle to see the Orang Utan on their feeding time. After feeding the Orang Utan tracking through the Leuser National Park, walking around Leuser National Park is the time to experience many kinds of flora and fauna as well as enjoy the song of birds and Siamang? The Black Gibbon? and overnight in a tent or shelter.</div><div align=\"justify\"><b><br></b></div><div align=\"justify\"><b>DAY 03.CONTINUE TRACKING RETURN TO HOTEL (B.L)</b></div><div align=\"justify\">breakfast prepared by tour guide continue tracking, today is full day walking and explore the rain tropical forest with their wildlife living in their natural habitat. Afternoon return to the hotel.</div><div align=\"justify\"><br></div><div align=\"justify\"><b>DAY 04. FULLDAY WHITE WATER RAFTING (B.L.)</b></div><div align=\"justify\">After breakfast drive by minibus to Wampu river and arrival at the starting point, starting your white water rafting adventure. During the rafting, the excellent opportunity to see the bird and wildlife as white enjoying the two mild rapids. Arrival at waterfall at the bank of the river enjoying your shower and lunch will be provided afternoon arrival at the point stop enjoying a coffee break before driving back to the hotel.</div><div align=\"justify\"><br></div><div align=\"justify\"><b>DAY 05. BUKIT LAWANG FREE AT OWN LEISURE. B</b></div><div align=\"justify\">Today is a free time to enjoy the view of Bukit Lawang, walking to the villages or relaxing.</div><div align=\"justify\"><br></div><div align=\"justify\"><b>DAY 06. BUKIT LAWANG - MEDAN.(EMERALD GARDEN / ASEAN INT HTL /SIMILAR) B.</b></div><div align=\"justify\">After breakfast free at own leisure for swimming or walking and then drive to Medan arrival in Medan, city tour by visiting Great Mosque, Sultan Palace and Chinese Temple.</div><div align=\"justify\"><b><br></b></div><div align=\"justify\"><b>DAY 07. HOTEL - AIRPORT.B.</b></div><div align=\"justify\">After breakfast transfer to Airport for your flight to the next destination.</div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                ');
