tages / Rindu Alam Hotel / similar)Â Â  (B)</b><br>After breakfast leave Tangkahan for Bukit Lawang by Jeep passing plantations and jungle road, on the way stop at several interesting places (school) for enjoying the panorama and witness the activities of the local people. Upon arrival at Bukit Lawang check-in to hotel and afternoon free at own leisure to enjoy the nature of Bukit Lawang.<br><br><b>DAY 05: FULLDAY LEUSER NATIONAL PARK TRACKINGÂ  (B,L)</b><br>After breakfast walking to the jungle to start a jungle tracking to explore the nature of Leuser National Park with its flora and fauna, there will be possibility to see Orang Utan on their own habitat and other kind of animals such as Thomas-leaf monkeys, long tail maccaque, gibbon, black gibbon and other kind of flora and fauna of tropical rain-forest. This full day tracking will finish in the afternoon. <br><br><b>DAY 06: BUKIT LAWANG â€“ MEDAN / AIRPORTÂ Â  (B)</b><br>After breakfast drive to Medan via Binjai, on the way visiting traditional market at Kuala, arrival in Medan directly transfer to Kualanamu International Airport for your flight to next destination.<br></div><br><div align=\"justify\"><b>Included:</b><br>-Accommodation in twin sharing<br>-Air condition private car<br>-Daily breakfast<br>-Tours<br>-Transfers<br>-Entrance fee<br>-English speaking tour guide<br>-Elephant washing + elephant feeding at Tangkahan<br>-Tubing at Tangkahan + picnic lunch<br>-Local non-aircon jeep for transfer from Tangkahan to Bukit Lawang<br>-Fullday jungle tracking at Bukit Lawang included: local guide, permit and picnic lunch<br><br><b>Excluded:</b><br>-Airfare, airport taxes, insurance, donation, tips, lunch, dinner, elephant riding at Tangkahan, camera permit at Bukit Lawang and all personal gratuities.<br></div><br>                                                                                                                                                                                                          